                     <interp inst="t18420822-2209-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18420822-2209-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp> for stealing, on the 11th of July, 1 handkerchief, value 1<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18420822-name-214" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18420822-name-214" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
